 6. the french is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the egyptian is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
