The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, snowboarding, water-polo
 1. the person eating mango is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing backgammon is between the person watching family movies and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the person eating potato##1
13. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
