 9. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
10. the fan of gospel is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's birthday is in november##2
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

